lass=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104voy1665703134785.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/voy1665703134785.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/voy1665703134785.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"voy1665703134785\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"voy1665703134785__ulist_uf_405303\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Copy item list data to a basic parameter or entity field.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"voy1665703134785__topic_d121739e1_d121740e1_d121741e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104voy1665703134785_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"voy1665703134785__codeblock_mds_vwc_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long ulist2uf (UHACT hOpr, int seqNr, UHACT hList);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"voy1665703134785__topic_d86322e1_d86323e1_d86324e1_d86325e1_d86326e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d930345e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"voy1665703134785__parml_lgz_wwc_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hOpr</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">The handle to an operation of entity parameter</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">seqNr</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">The sequence number of the basic parameter or entity field</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hList</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">The handle to the list, as returned by <code class=\"ph codeph\">ulistnew</code></dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"voy1665703134785__topic_d86327e1_d86328e1_d86329e1_d86330e1_d86331e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d930345e102\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"voy1665703134785__d5955e20\">For more information, see the \"Call-In API Return\n        Codes\" topic.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"voy1665703134785__topic_d86332e1_d86333e1_d86334e1_d86335e1_d86336e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d930345e111\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"voy1665703134785__d5956e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ucall</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"voy1665703134785__topic_d86337e1_d86338e1_d86339e1_d86340e1_d86341e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d930345e123\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"voy1665703134785__p_d121772e1_d121773e1_d121774e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ulist2uf</code> copies the data from an item list (created by\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">ulistnew</code> and populated by <code class=\"ph codeph\">ulistput</code>) into a basic\n            parameter or entity field.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"voy1665703134785__section_ohx_1xc_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d930345e141\">Example: ulistnew, ulist2uf, ulistdel, and ulistput</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example creates an associative list, consisting of country\n            codes and names, and passes it to a service, which prints it to the message frame. The\n            operation DOLIST in service TESTSVC is defined as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104voy1665703134785_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"voy1665703134785__codeblock_ast_cxc_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation dolist\nparams\nstring thelist : in;\nendparams\nputmess \"%%thelist\"\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The 3GL code that creates the list and passes it to service DOLIST is as\n            follows:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104voy1665703134785_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"voy1665703134785__codeblock_urq_2xc_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">char *countries[] = {\n\n\"NL\", \"Netherlands\",\n\"GB\", \"Great Britain\",\n\"D\", \"Germany\",\n\"F\", \"France\",\n\"?\", \"huh?\",\n\"I\", \"Italy\",\n\"E\", \"Spain\",\n0 };\n\n#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nvoid pass_itemlist ()\n{\nUHACT hEnv, hIn; /* Environment and instance handle */\nUHACT hOp; /* Operation handles for OP1 amd OP2 */\nlong actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */\nUHACT hList; /* Item list handle */\nint i; /* Loop variable */\n\nueopen(&amp;hEnv); /* Get environment handle */\nuinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"TESTSVC\", 0, 0,\nUDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &amp;hIn, &amp;procErr);/* Instantiate service TESTSVC */\n\nuinstopr (hIn, (UCHAR *)\"DOLIST\", 0, &amp;hOp);/* Instantiate operation DOLIST*/\nulistnew(hEnv, &amp;hList); /* Create an item list */\n\nfor ( i=0; countries[i]; i+= 2 ) /* Loop through the data */\n{\nulistput(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0,\ncountries[i], countries[i+1] ); /* Add the list item */\n}\n\nulistdel(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0, \"?\");/* Delete the item with id \"?\" */\nulist2uf(hOp, 1, hList); /* Copy item list to operation param*/\nuopract(hOp, &amp;actStatus, &amp;procErr); /* Activate the operation */\n\nuinstdel (hIn, 0); /* Destroy instance */\nufreeh (&amp;hList); /* Free list handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hOp); /* Free operation handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hIn); /* Free instance handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hEnv); /* Free environment handle */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The operation DOLIST will print this line to the message frame</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104voy1665703134785_html_3\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"voy1665703134785__codeblock_pbp_hxc_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">NL=Netherlands;GB=Great Britain;D=Germany;F=France;I=Italy;E=Spain</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jhh1665702691902.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Call-In API Return Codes</a><p>Codes that can possibly be returned by functions from the 3GL call-in API are consistent with the values returned by the ProcScript function $procerror, unless noted otherwise.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yia1665702692785.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ulistnew</a><p>Create an item list.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nci1665702692918.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ulistput</a><p>Insert an item into an item list.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fln1665703134854.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uuf2list</a><p>Copy list data from a basic parameter or entity field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533113\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533113\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ulist2uf Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Copy item list data to a basic parameter or entity field. Explain this code long ulist2uf (UHACT hOpr, int seqNr, UHACT hList); Copy Parameters hOpr The handle to an operation of entity parameter seqNr The sequence number of the basic parameter or entity field hList The handle to the list, as returned by ulistnew Return Values For more information, see the \"Call-In API Return Codes\" topic. Use Library: ucall Description ulist2uf copies the data from an item list (created by ulistnew and populated by ulistput ) into a basic parameter or entity field. Example: ulistnew, ulist2uf, ulistdel, and ulistput The following example creates an associative list, consisting of country codes and names, and passes it to a service, which prints it to the message frame. The operation DOLIST in service TESTSVC is defined as follows: Explain this code operation dolist params string thelist : in; endparams putmess \"%%thelist\" end Copy The 3GL code that creates the list and passes it to service DOLIST is as follows: Explain this code char *countries[] = { \"NL\", \"Netherlands\", \"GB\", \"Great Britain\", \"D\", \"Germany\", \"F\", \"France\", \"?\", \"huh?\", \"I\", \"Italy\", \"E\", \"Spain\", 0 }; #include <h3gl.h> void pass_itemlist () { UHACT hEnv, hIn; /* Environment and instance handle */ UHACT hOp; /* Operation handles for OP1 amd OP2 */ long actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */ UHACT hList; /* Item list handle */ int i; /* Loop variable */ ueopen(&hEnv); /* Get environment handle */ uinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"TESTSVC\", 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &hIn, &procErr);/* Instantiate service TESTSVC */ uinstopr (hIn, (UCHAR *)\"DOLIST\", 0, &hOp);/* Instantiate operation DOLIST*/ ulistnew(hEnv, &hList); /* Create an item list */ for ( i=0; countries[i]; i+= 2 ) /* Loop through the data */ { ulistput(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0, countries[i], countries[i+1] ); /* Add the list item */ } ulistdel(hList, UITEM_OPTION_ID, 0, \"?\");/* Delete the item with id \"?\" */ ulist2uf(hOp, 1, hList); /* Copy item list to operation param*/ uopract(hOp, &actStatus, &procErr); /* Activate the operation */ uinstdel (hIn, 0); /* Destroy instance */ ufreeh (&hList); /* Free list handle */ ufreeh (&hOp); /* Free operation handle */ ufreeh (&hIn); /* Free instance handle */ ufreeh (&hEnv); /* Free environment handle */ } Copy The operation DOLIST will print this line to the message frame Explain this code NL=Netherlands;GB=Great Britain;D=Germany;F=France;I=Italy;E=Spain Copy Related Links Call-In API Return Codes Codes that can possibly be returned by functions from the 3GL call-in API are consistent with the values returned by the ProcScript function $procerror, unless noted otherwise. ulistnew Create an item list. ulistput Insert an item into an item list. uuf2list Copy list data from a basic parameter or entity field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}